=== T006: Schema $comment field cites canonical-form rule + trust-root construction ===
--- Extract $comment from contracts/manifest.schema.json ---
Canonical-form serialization rule (per pocketnet-node-doctor pre-spec Implementation Context): sorted JSON keys at every nesting level, no insignificant whitespace (no spaces between tokens, no trailing newline inside the serialized payload), UTF-8 byte output. The trust-root constant for a canonical is SHA-256(canonical_form_serialize(this manifest)) — externally published as the sidecar file 'trust-root.sha256' next to 'manifest.json'. The trust-root is NOT carried inside the manifest. Both the server-side manifest generator and the doctor-side plan-format library MUST serialize using this rule so the hashes are reproducible across implementations.
